# ğŸ“¢ POSIX Compliance Guidelines:
# âœ… Use `[` instead of `[[` for conditions
# âœ… Use `$(command)` instead of backticks `` `command` ``
# âœ… Use `$(( ))` for arithmetic instead of `let`
# âœ… Define functions as `func_name() {}` (no `function` keyword)
